Evidence facets:
- `operator_or_project_profile`: an identity-centered public profile, official/project disclosure, announcement, or comparable public presence source that confirms the exact named organization/facility's hatching-chain role.
- `external_supply_or_genetics_link`: a relationship-centered external input, import, foreign breeder/genetics source, named breed or genetics line, parent/grandparent-stock supply, supplier/distributor relationship, or comparable external-supply/genetics link centered on the exact named organization/facility or that named relationship.
