The organization or facility should be a named public organization, operator, project, farm, hatchery, breeder farm, genetics distributor, parent-stock operator, day-old-chick producer, hatching-egg/day-old-chick supplier, importer/distributor, or comparable entity/facility tied to the listed country. A named farm, hatchery, breeder site, production site, branch, project component, product line, or subfacility counts as its own identity only when the cited evidence gives that component its own public hatching-chain facts; a parent operator, project, distributor network, or funder page can qualify the parent operator/project/network identity, but not each listed component facility by itself. Generic poultry farms or livestock businesses count only when the cited source states hatching egg, day-old chick, hatchery, breeder/parent-stock, poultry genetics, external supply/import, capacity, or distribution facts for the named entity/facility. Generic country-level trade statistics, broad market commentary, broad multi-entity sector reports or comparative tables without a named entity/project-centered passage, generic breed-performance documents, generic poultry advice, paid shipment mirrors, RFQ/buyer-contact directories, lead databases, marketplaces, bare contact pages, freight-rate pages, and procurement/ranking/listicle pages are not enough as evidence. Contacts, buyer/supplier rankings, prices, freight guarantees, outreach, import strategy, finance advice, sanitary/legal/compliance advice, source-class labels, checked dates, confidence, source-date bookkeeping, and no-source/no-date/no-import/no-volume/no-freight flags are outside the evidence being sought.

Requirements:
- The page must clearly identify the named organization/facility.
- The page must match the exact identity level being claimed: organization/operator/project identities need organization/operator/project-centered evidence; named farms, hatcheries, breeder sites, production sites, branches, product lines, or subfacilities need a passage or section specifically centered on that component. A broad parent, project, network, distributor, or funder page that merely lists several component sites does not satisfy this requirement for each component.
- The page must tie the organization/facility to the listed country.
- The page must visibly earn the facet-specific source role through its content or context: for `operator_or_project_profile`, an organization/operator-controlled channel, official project or facility page, public funder/government disclosure, industry-press profile, or comparable public profile surface centered on the exact named organization/facility or its project; for `external_supply_or_genetics_link`, a direct external-supply/genetics relationship surface such as a counterparty-controlled breeder/supplier/distributor profile, relationship-specific announcement, operator disclosure centered on the named input or line, or project/news disclosure centered on the named external link; for `capacity_or_distribution_signal`, an exact-identity capacity, output, investment, project-scale, distribution-footprint, or market-supply surface such as an operator page, official project/facility page, public funder/development disclosure, government/program page, or relationship-specific industry/news source. A broad report, directory, parent-project page, distributor page, or table that only gives the entity/facility as one item among many does not earn these source roles by itself.
- The page must state a concrete exact-scope facet finding: for `operator_or_project_profile`, the entity's own role in the hatching egg / day-old chick / hatchery / breeder / parent-stock / poultry genetics chain; for `external_supply_or_genetics_link`, the external input, import, foreign breeder/genetics source, named line, parent/grandparent-stock supply, or supplier/distributor relationship for that exact entity; for `capacity_or_distribution_signal`, the output, throughput, capacity, project scale, distribution footprint, market-supply role, or comparable scale/distribution signal for that exact entity.
